        "Client": "Lord\u0027s Aide",
        "Description": "Oh dear... The lord\u0027s son heard\r\na Great Wroggi was in the Flooded\r\nForest and went out to hunt it. What\r\na fool. Surely he\u0027ll run at the first\r\nsign of danger. Can you hunt the\r\ncreature before my lord gets hurt.",
